<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>myn gẖyrk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- myn gẖyrk ʿạrf nfsy kl mạfyhạ tmạm
 ʿạrf fkry wạlly fy qlby msẖ mḥtạj lklạm
 myn gẖyrk yqdr ywṣl lldạʾ fy ạ̉ʿmạqy
 tsẖfy wtdwạy tʿṣb wtrjʿ ạ̉frạḥy
 ạlqrạr - ạlnạs mḥtạjẗ ʿyạn wdlạỷl mʿ brhạn
 lknk yạ ḥbyby msẖ mḥtạj lbyạn
 2- wạ̹n sẖft ạlẓlm fy ywm blqạk rby ạlgẖạly
 sẖbʿy wrạḥty wạ̉mly wgẖạyty fy kl ạ̉ḥwạly
 ly fyk ạltʿwyḍ wạlfrḥ wạlslạm
 ḥty̱ lw ạldnyạ ẓlạm nwrk mạly ạlạ̉yạm</lyrics>
